MegaList
********

   MegaList manual updated: 14 June 1995

   MegaList is a filelisting utilitiy for the Xenolink BBS. The program
is able to produce filelists and the add/update them to the
filecatalouge.  You can also create AmigaGuide-compatible filelists!


 @{" Copying " Link "Copying"}                         Distribution rights.
 @{" Requirements " Link "Requirements"}                    Hardware & software requirements.
 @{" Installation " Link "Installation"}                    How to install MegaList.
 @{" Configuration " Link "Configuration"}                   Description of MegaList.cfg.
 @{" MegaList usage " Link "MegaList usage"}                  Using MegaList.
 @{" Registration " Link "Registration"}                    How to encourage the author.
 @{" Bugreports " Link "Bugreports"}                      Please send them!
 @{" Acknowledgements " Link "Acknowledgements"} 


@EndNode

